dct_title_s: Andrews's new and accurate travelling map of the kingdom of Ireland divided into provinces & counties with all the cities ... turnpike and principal cross roads, with the distance in Irish miles from town to town
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows distances between individual cities. Title from Bibliothèque nationale de France.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Sold & publish'd as the Act directs ... by John Andrews No. 29 Long Acre and John Harris No. 3, Sweetings Alley Cornhill, July 3d. 1781.
